title: Serialize/Whitespace-normalized
description: AST-only mode normalizes token spacing
tags: $:/tags/wikitext-serialize-normalize-spec
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki-multiple

title: info

`\\whitespace     trim` becomes `\whitespace trim`: the token spacing
collapses to single spaces.

Why: the pragma's void marker node carries the keyword list, but not the
spacing between the tokens.

* Covers: $:/plugins/tiddlywiki/wikitext-serialize/rules/whitespace.js.
* Mode: ast-only (the Input field withholds the source from the serializer).
+
title: Input
mode: ast-only

\whitespace     trim

Some text.
+
title: ExpectedWikitext

\whitespace trim

Some text.
